---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQSchema from "../../../components/FAQSchema.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Residential Carpet Cleaning | Montreal, Laval, South Shore"
  description="Professional residential carpet cleaning at home. Wool, synthetic, and oriental rugs. Elimination of stains and dust mites. Montreal, Laval & South Shore. Free quote."
>
  <!-- SPLIT SCREEN HERO (Standardized) -->
  <div class="split-hero-container">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: CONTENT -->
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">CARPETS & RUGS</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Residential Carpet Cleaning
          </h1>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100">
            <h3 class="problem-title">The Problem:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              Carpets act as the largest filter in your home. They trap dust, allergens, pet dander, and absorb spills. Over time, fibers become crushed, colors fade, and odors settle in. Vacuuming alone only removes surface dirt.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            Revive your carpets with our deep <strong>steam extraction</strong>. Using high-powered truck-mounted units, we flush out embedded dirt, kill dust mites, and restore the original softness and vibrant colors of your carpets directly at your home.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-primary pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939
            </a>
            <button onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()" class="btn btn-outline-reveal">
              <span class="icon">⚡</span> Instant Free Quote
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: IMAGE (Carousel) -->
        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-9.webp"
              alt="High pressure carpet cleaning residential Montreal - Empire Group"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              fetchpriority="high"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-15.webp"
              alt="Deep steam carpet extraction - Laval"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-27.webp"
              alt="Stain removal on white residential carpet"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-115.webp"
              alt="Professional carpet washer equipment"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-140.webp"
              alt="Carpet cleaning technician South Shore"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-138.webp"
              alt="Stairs carpet cleaning - Montreal"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-150.webp"
              alt="Before After carpet cleaning results"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/rug-cleaning-optimized.webp"
              alt="Area rug cleaning at home Montreal"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container alternate-layout">
      <div class="service-main-content">
        
        <div class="info-block">
          <h2 class="text-gradient-empire">Why choose professional truck-mounted equipment?</h2>
          <p>Renting a small carpet cleaner from the grocery store often does more harm than good. These machines lack the suction power to extract the water they spray, leaving your carpets soaked for days. This breeds mold and mildew, permanently damaging the padding underneath.</p>
          <p>Our <strong>industrial truck-mounted units</strong> generate water temperatures exceeding 200°F and possess vacuum suction 20 times stronger than portable machines. We extract 95% of the moisture instantly, alongside years of accumulated grime, leaving your carpets fresh and dry within hours.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Types of carpets & rugs we treat</h3>
          <p>Not all fibers react the same way to water and heat. Our certified technicians identify your carpet type before selecting the appropriate cleaning method:</p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li><strong>Wall-to-wall carpeting:</strong> Living rooms, bedrooms, basements, and staircases.</li>
            <li><strong><a href="/en/services/tapis-synthetique" style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Synthetic Fibers (Nylon, Polyester):</a></strong> Extremely durable; responds exceptionally well to high-heat steam extraction.</li>
            <li><strong><a href="/en/services/tapis-laine" style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Wool & Natural Fibers:</a></strong> Requires lower temperatures, specialized wool-safe detergents, and rapid drying to prevent shrinkage and browning.</li>
            <li><strong><a href="/en/services/tapis-orientaux" style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Oriental & Persian Rugs:</a></strong> Gentle hand-cleaning methods focusing on color stability and fringe restoration.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- PROCESSUS -->
        <div class="process-section" style="margin-top: 4rem;">
          <h2 class="text-gradient-empire">Our 5-Step Deep Cleaning Process</h2>
          <div class="process-steps">
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>Pre-Inspection & Vacuuming</h3>
                <p>We examine the carpet to identify high-traffic areas, specific stains, and fiber type, followed by a thorough commercial dry vacuuming to remove loose dirt.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>Pre-Conditioning</h3>
                <p>We apply a specialized eco-friendly solution to break down oils, grease, and spots before the main cleaning begins.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>Hot Water Extraction (Steam Cleaning)</h3>
                <p>High-pressure hot water (up to 230°F) is injected into the carpet fibers, instantly dislodging dirt, which is simultaneously vacuumed out by our powerful truck-mount system.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>Spot Handling & Neutralizing</h3>
                <p>Stubborn stains receive targeted treatment. We then apply a pH-balancing rinse to ensure the carpet feels soft and doesn't attract dirt quickly post-cleaning.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-num">5</div>
              <div class="step-text">
                <h3>Grooming & Drying</h3>
                <p>The fibers are gently groomed in one direction to restore their standing position, improving appearance and speeding up the natural drying process.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- PROTECTEUR CTA -->
        <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background: #fffdf0; border-left: 4px solid #fbc02d; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
           <h4 style="color: #856404; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem;">🛡️ Maximize your investment with Stain Protection</h4>
           <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem;">After a deep clean, the factory-applied protective coating is often worn away by foot traffic and the washing process itself. We highly recommend adding a <a href="/en/services/protecteur" style="color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Teflon or Scotchgard carpet protector</a>.</p>
           <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">It creates an invisible shield around every fiber, repelling liquids, preventing dry soil from sticking, and making your next vacuuming much more effective.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- SERVICED ZONES -->
        <div class="zones-section" style="margin-top: 4rem;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">Service Areas — Residential Carpet Cleaning</h3>
          <p>We travel anywhere in the Greater Montreal Area with our high-performance mobile units.</p>

          <div class="city-group">
            <p class="city-lead">🏙️ Montreal (East & West)</p>
            <div class="badges-container">
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Montreal (all boroughs)</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Westmount</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Mount Royal</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Outremont</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 LaSalle</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 And much more...</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="city-group">
            <p class="city-lead">🏘️ Laval</p>
            <div class="badges-container">
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Laval (entire city)</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Chomedey</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Sainte-Rose</span>
              <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Vimont</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="city-group">
            <p class="city-lead">🌿 Montreal South Shore</p>
            <div class="badges-container">
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Longueuil</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Brossard</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Saint-Lambert</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Saint-Hubert</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Greenfield Park</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Saint-Bruno</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 Boucherville</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">📍 And much more...</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="contact-footer">Need a quick appointment? Call us at <strong>(514) 893-9939</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ with Schema Component -->
        <FAQSchema
          title="Frequently Asked Questions"
          faqs={[
              {
                question: "How long does it take for carpets to dry after steam cleaning?",
                answer: "With our industrial truck-mounted extraction system, carpets generally dry in 4 to 8 hours. The exact time depends on the style of carpet, air circulation, and humidity levels in your home. We recommend turning on fans or air conditioning to expedite the process.",
              },
              {
                question: "Do I need to move all my furniture before you arrive?",
                answer: "We ask that you remove small items (lamps, plants, electronics, breakables, toys) from the areas to be cleaned. Our technicians will carefully move light furniture (sofas, chairs, tables) as they clean, placing protective tabs underneath the legs before replacing them. We do not move very heavy items like pianos, loaded bookcases, or large beds.",
              },
              {
                question: "Will all the stains come out?",
                answer: "We carry a full arsenal of professional stain removers and succeed where consumer products fail. However, some substances may permanently discolor or dye the carpet fibers (e.g., bleach spills, old urine stains that have oxidized, certain dyes in food). We cannot guarantee the removal of permanent dyes, but we promise a significant improvement and a completely sanitized carpet.",
              },
              {
                question: "How often should I have my carpets professionally cleaned?",
                answer: "Major carpet manufacturers (like Mohawk and Shaw) strongly recommend hot water extraction every 12 to 18 months to maintain your warranty. If you have indoor pets, children, or suffer from indoor allergies, cleaning every 6 to 9 months is advisable.",
              },
              {
                question: "Are your cleaning products safe for my pets and babies?",
                answer: "Absolutely. We prioritize the health of your family. Our main pre-sprays and detergents are eco-friendly, non-toxic, and biodegradable. Furthermore, our thorough extraction process ensures no harmful soapy residues are left behind in the fibers.",
              },
              {
                question: "What is the dark lines around the edge of my carpet near the baseboards?",
                answer: "This is known as 'filtration soiling'. It happens when air is forced through the gap between the carpet and baseboard (or under doors), leaving microscopic airborne particles trapped in the carpet fibers. These are very fine particles of soot and dust that are notoriously difficult to remove completely, though our specialized treatments can lighten them significantly.",
              },
              {
                 question: "My dog peed on the carpet several times, can you get the smell out?",
                 answer: "Yes. Standard cleaning won't fix urine odor because the uric acid crystals penetrate deeply into the padding and even the subfloor. We offer specialized pet odor treatments involving enzyme injections that digest the odor-causing bacteria at the source. Please inform us of the issue when booking so we can allocate the right treatment.",
              },
              {
                 question: "Can you clean area rugs (Oriental, Persian) in my home?",
                 answer: "Yes, we clean most area rugs directly in your home. However, genuine hand-woven Oriental, Persian, or high-end natural fiber rugs require specialized low-moisture treatments to prevent color bleeding and shrinkage. We assess each rug on-site to determine the safest and most effective method.",
              }
            ]}
          />
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- SIDEBAR -->
      <aside class="service-sidebar">
        <div class="sticky-cta">
          <h3>Free Estimate</h3>
          <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-primary full-width">(514) 893-9939</a>
          <button onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()" class="btn btn-outline full-width">Online Estimate</button>
          <div class="guarantee">⭐ 100% Satisfaction Guarantee</div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* HERO SPLIT LAYOUT (Standardized) */
  .split-hero-container {
    background-color: #fff;
    padding-top: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    width: 100vw;
  }
  .full-width-split { width: 100%; max-width: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .split-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: stretch;
    min-height: 80vh;
  }
  .split-content {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .service-cat-badge {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .split-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 3.5vw, 3.8rem);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .problem-statement {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-left: 4px solid #ff4444;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3);
  }
  .problem-title { font-size: 1rem; color: #cc0000; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; }
  .problem-text { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-main); font-style: italic; }
  .lead-text { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-main); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 650px; }
  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .split-image-wrapper { position: relative; height: 100%; min-height: 500px; width: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  .slideshow-container { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  .slide { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out; }
  .slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  .image-overlay-gradient { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.2), transparent); pointer-events: none; z-index: 2; }

  /* BUTTON STYLES (Standardized) */
  .btn-outline-reveal {
    background: transparent; border: 2px solid var(--color-primary); color: var(--color-primary);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; cursor: pointer;
    border-radius: 4px; transition: all 0.3s ease; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .btn-outline-reveal:hover { background: var(--color-primary); color: white; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .content-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .alternate-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 350px; gap: 4rem; }
  .info-block h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .info-block p { line-height: 1.7; color: #444; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .check-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .check-list li { padding: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem 1.75rem; position: relative; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }
  .check-list li::before { content: "✓"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #2e7d32; font-weight: bold; }

  /* ZONES */
  .city-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .city-lead { font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .badges-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .badge { padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .badge-blue { background: #e8f4fd; border-color: #c5dff0; }
  .badge-green { background: #f0faf0; border-color: #b8ddb8; }
  .contact-footer { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; }

  /* PROCESS */
  .process-steps { margin-top: 2rem; }
  .step { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .step-num { min-width: 32px; height: 32px; background: var(--color-primary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 5px; }
  .step-text h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .step-text p { color: #555; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* SIDEBAR */
  .sticky-cta { position: sticky; top: 100px; background: white; border: 1px solid #eee; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); text-align: center; }
  .sticky-cta h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .sticky-cta p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .guarantee { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: bold; color: #2e7d32; }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .alternate-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .split-title { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .split-image-wrapper { height: 400px; min-height: 0; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Slideshow Logic
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
  let currentSlide = 0;

  function nextSlide() {
    slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
    currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
    slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
  }

  if (slides.length > 1) {
    setInterval(nextSlide, 4000); // 4 seconds
  }
</script>
